00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Here's a quiz.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Five guys and a monkey are stranded on an island.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
On the island are many coconut trees with many coconuts.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:16.000
The guys and the monkeys spend all day collecting a huge pile of coconuts.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.000
When night falls, they are all very tired except for the monkey,

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:27.000
and they all fall asleep after they agree 

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.000
to divide the divide the coconuts into 5 equals part the next morning

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
and part different ways.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Now, in the middle of the night the first guy wakes up,

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:41.000
and he doesn't trust the others, so he decides to take his 5th right now and hide it,

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:48.000
but unfortunately, the number of coconuts is not divisible by 5.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.000
However, if he gives one to the monkey, then the remainder is divisible by 5.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:57.000
So he takes his 5th and hides it in a safe place.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Afterward the guy falls asleep again.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
The same scene now repeats 4 more times for each of the guys.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:11.000
